items.title: More than 10 European startups became unicorns this year

items.title: With India’s corporate banking lagging decades behind consumer fintech, TransBnk raises $25M to bridge the gap

items.title: Maisa AI gets $25M to fix enterprise AI’s 95% failure rate

items.description: The exodus has set off alarms among staff at the US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention: “My main concern is they will be replaced with puppets...

items.title: Nvidia reports record sales as the AI boom continues
items.description: Nvidia's revenue hit $46.7 billion in the second quarter, a 56% increase compared to the same period last year.

items.title: This Is the Group That's Been Swatting US Universities
